Cyril Ramaphosa to appear before the State Capture Inquiry in April. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa will be appearing before the State Capture Inquiry in April Ramaphosa will testify in his capacity as President of the country. WATCH: State capture inquiry gets heated The announcement was made by the commission's chairperson, Deputy Chief Justice Raymond Zondo on Wednesday. Watch the video above.